{"id":225232,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/05/新浪禁止隐晦表达/","date":"2012-05-09T06:20:31Z","modified":"2012-05-09T06:25:48Z","title":"新浪禁止隐晦表达","content":"<p>在发生被某些人认为具有敏感性的新闻或事件之后，为了绕过审查机制，网友常常会借助谐音或发明新表达方法去隐晦阐述其看法或传播新闻。然而现在，中国最大的微博服务新浪说不许隐晦表达。新浪公布了社区公约，称帐号信息不能违反国家法律法规、包含人身攻击性质内容等，“不得使用隐晦表达等方式规避以上限制”。新浪对发贴内容进行限制，并建立审查内容的社区委员会，以及对违规行为的惩罚，如“累计发布5条及以上敏感信息的用户，禁言48小时；恶意发布敏感信息的用户，禁言48小时以上，甚至注销帐号”。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1f2545d7/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&#038;title=%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%9A%90%E6%99%A6%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F05%2F09%2F0215227%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%9A%90%E6%99%A6%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F05%2F09%2F0215227%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/133515425671/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1f2545d7/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/133515425671/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1f2545d7/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/133515425671/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1f2545d7/a2t.img\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=QLxFFoxahyw:lUb5BAFiDEM:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=QLxFFoxahyw:lUb5BAFiDEM:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?